title: The Sholan Alliance - Lisanne Norman
description:
The Sholan Alliance Series consists of these books:

Turning Point
Fortune's Wheel
Fire Margins 
Razor's Edge
Dark Nadir
Stronghold Rising
Between Darkness and Light
Shades of Gray

Not Included:
AVATAR (In production.)


The Sholan Alliance Series is a series of science-fiction novels written by author Lisanne Norman. Eight books in the series have been released so far; there is another book planned
